## Risk Assessment

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Fixing auth bypass breaks local dev workflows | Medium | Medium | Provide `make dev` or `.env.dev` that explicitly opts into unsafe mode |
| Deleting `validator_keys.json` breaks dev scripts | Low | Medium | Replace with generated fixture; update scripts to call generator |
| B023 fix changes blockchain behavior unexpectedly | Low | High | Add multi-chain integration test before fix; review diff carefully |
| Mypy baseline hides real bugs | Medium | Medium | Baseline is temporary; sprint to shrink exclusions each release |
| CI tool consolidation breaks existing workflows | Medium | Low | Test new install path in a feature branch first |
| Moving `mutants/` breaks mutation-test reporting | Low | Low | Update CI artifact upload path; verify dashboard links |
| Disabling docs in production breaks API consumers | Low | Medium | Announce change; provide static OpenAPI JSON export as replacement |
| Removing default secrets breaks unconfigured dev environments | Medium | Low | Add `scripts/setup_dev_secrets.py` that generates random local secrets |
| Module split breaks existing imports | Medium | Medium | Keep re-export aliases in old modules during deprecation window |
| Decimal migration breaks serialization | Medium | High | Add comprehensive regression tests for token math before merge |
| Sanitizing 500s hides debugging info | Low | Medium | Ensure server-side logs retain full tracebacks with request IDs |
| Async task registry crashes on shutdown | Low | Medium | Graceful cancellation with timeout; log failures but do not hang |
| Timezone-aware timestamps break SQLite queries | Low | Medium | Test timestamp comparison logic in SQLite/PostgreSQL after migration |
| Consolidating DB modules breaks app startup | Medium | High | Run coordinator-api integration tests before and after consolidation |
| Duplicate-route guard breaks intentionally shadowed routes | Low | Medium | Review all duplicate `include_router` calls first; only keep intentional overrides |
| Gating mock routes breaks internal test clients | Medium | Medium | Update test `conftest.py` to set `ENABLE_MOCK_*=1`; document flag usage |
| Replacing `_mock_*` globals with DB breaks unit-test speed | Medium | Low | Use an in-memory SQLite or Redis for test fixtures; keep DB layer thin |
| Adding response_model to all endpoints causes serialization regressions | Medium | High | Add endpoints incrementally; run integration tests after each batch |
| Auth normalization breaks blockchain RPC clients | Medium | High | Maintain backward-compatible `X-Wallet-Address` header during transition period |
| Removing double-prefix paths breaks existing client URLs | Medium | Medium | Announce path changes; add 308 redirects for one release cycle |
| Mock crypto removal breaks demo scripts | Low | Low | Move demo content to `examples/` with explicit `debug=True` requirement |
| OpenAPI CI check flakes on optional router load order | Low | Low | Generate spec after all routers are loaded; use deterministic startup order |
| Consolidating dependency files breaks app installs | Medium | Medium | Test install path on a fresh VM/container before merging |
| Python constraint alignment breaks older app installs | Low | Low | Ensure minimum is still `>=3.13`; only tighten upper bounds |
| Systemd hardening breaks services that need root access | Medium | High | Audit each service's actual FS needs; use `ReadWritePaths=` granularly |
| Moving secrets to env files breaks existing deploy scripts | Medium | Medium | Update setup scripts in same PR; provide migration guide |
| Removing `|| true` from recovery makes transient failures fatal | Low | Medium | Retry logic inside the script before final exit; fail only on persistent errors |
| ShellCheck fixes change script semantics | Low | Medium | Review each ShellCheck fix manually; test scripts in staging environment |
| Dry-run modes add complexity to scripts | Low | Low | Keep dry-run implementation simple (print commands, skip execution) |
| Observability consolidation loses custom metrics | Low | Medium | Map old metric names to new ones; maintain alias labels during transition |
| Telemetry bind lockdown breaks sidecar collectors | Low | Medium | Document required bind addresses; whitelist in CI check |

